node.text:
The Salt Cave at @islandwellnesscenter is my favorite spot to chill in Rhode Island! 

It’s so magical! 🥰

You can reserve your own private time at the Island Wellness Center:

 420 friendly for after hours! ✨

Weeknights 6-8pm and weekends 4-6pm. 

📸: @caseysanginario

node.text:
HELLO FRIENDSSSSSS!!!

Guess who’s back? 🎉 
UHUUUUUUUUUUUU!!! I just want to say that I’ll never forget who really showed me support while my page was disabled. I’m really grateful for you guys! 🥺❤️
Also OH MY GOD I can’t believe my page was disabled for almost two weeks!
Instagram is coming hard on cannabis accounts and it really sucks. Not being able to access my account after working 3 years for it was really frustrating. 

But… it’s really good to be back and I hope it stays 💕 

Follow my backup page in case I ever get deleted again @official_weedqueen 

I love you y’all! ❤️

#weedqueenofficial #rhodeisland #braziliangirl
